{"tid":893610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想嬲一個fd, 但份人太唔記仇,明明係想嬲佢耐d 都唔得","createTime":"2018-11-07T18:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T03:42:30.000Z","uid":157923,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5403456556146e99a1832879861e3a83f9b02cd1","tid":893610,"uid":157923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"仲諗住嬲到下年農歷新年先搵番佢<br />\n點知我過咗2個鐘已經覺得無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都係咁<br />\n啲人話咁記仇咪搞到自己咁辛苦<br />\n但太唔識得記仇<br />\n咪搞到覺得自己好唔抵<br />\n明明真係受咗委屈又唔識嬲<br />\n明明係傷害了我<br />\n但因心軟而好快覺得冇野<br />\n又變咗另一種有少少負面既情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嬲既原因係<br />\n講好咗既野<br />\n因為佢自己問題反口<br />\n姐係無理人地感受喇<br />\n仲要講到自己都唔想咁<br />\n但你做咗喎<br />\n一次都算<br />\n仲要唔止一次<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界<br />\n一啲識得體諒 寛容 理解他人 重視他人感受既人真係好容易受到傷害<br />\n學識對不重視你既人：你點對我，我就點對番你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a68d0f82d22e848bb32cffbfe0bc68a94117bb4","tid":893610,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:29:45.000Z","msg":"好快你有下一次"},{"pid":"62c84e8b963c4795175a0ed73d611d59f40a44a1","tid":893610,"uid":157923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快你有下一次</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}